 x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x193iq5w xeuugli x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1lliihq x1fj9vlw xhslqc4 x1hx0egp x1pg5gke xjb2p0i xo1l8bm xl2ypbo x1ic7a3i" style="--x-fontSize: 12px; --x-lineHeight: 8.5313px; --x-8dd7yt: -0.0137em; --x-hxtmnb: 0.0137em;">Monday</span></div></div><div class="_ak8j"><div class="_ak8k"><span class="x78zum5 x1cy8zhl" title="‪Create a modern, responsive, and accessible church website that reflects a welcoming, peaceful, and spiritual atmosphere. The design should use soft colors, elegant typography, and meaningful imagery (cross, Bible, prayer, worship, community).
The website must be mobile-friendly, fast-loading, and easy to navigate for all age groups.
🎨 Design Requirements
4
* Clean and minimal layout
* Warm and inviting color palette (white, gold, beige, soft blue, or maroon)
* Large hero banner with church name and tagline
* Easy navigation menu
* Accessible fonts and good contrast
* Calm and spiritual visual tone
🏠 Pages to Include
1. Home Page
* Hero section with:
   * Church name
   * Tagline / verse
   * Service timings
   * “Join Us This Sunday” button
* Welcome message from the pastor
* Upcoming events preview
* Quick links to sermons, prayer requests, and contact
2. About Us
* Church history
* Vision and mission
* Statement of faith
* Leadership team (pastor, ministers, staff)
3. Ministries
Separate sections for:
* Youth ministry
* Women’s fellowship
* Men’s fellowship
* Children’s ministry
* Outreach / missions
Each ministry should have a short description and meeting details.
4. Sermons
* Sermon archive with:
   * Title
   * Speaker
   * Date
   * Bible passage
* Audio/video player
* Download option
* Search and filter by topic or book of the Bible
5. Events
* Upcoming events calendar
* Special services (Christmas, Easter, conferences, fasting prayer)
* Registration form for events
6. Gallery
* Photos of:
   * Worship services
   * Baptism
   * Outreach programs
   * Church gatherings
7. Prayer Request
* Secure form to submit prayer requests
* Option to mark as private
* Message: “We will pray for you”
8. Give / Donations
* Online giving options
* UPI / bank details
* Tithes and offerings information
* Scripture on giving
9. Contact Us
* Church address with Google Map
* Phone number
* Email
* Service timings
* Contact form
⚙️ Functional Requirements
* Mobile responsive design
* SEO-friendly structure
* Fast loading speed
* Social media links
* Newsletter subscription
* WhatsApp “Message Us” button
* Live streaming integration (YouTube/Facebook)
🔒 Accessibility &amp; UX
* Large readable fonts
* Alt text for images
* Simple navigation for elderly users
* Clear call-to-action buttons
📝 Content Tone
* Warm, welcoming, and faith-centered
* Scripture-based messaging
* Community-focused language
* Encouraging and inclusive
💻 Technical Suggestions (Optional)
If coding:
* Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (or React)
* Backend: Node.js / Django / PHP
* CMS option: WordPress for easy sermon uploads
* Database for sermons, events, and prayer requests
📌 Extra Features (Optional but Recommended)
* Daily verse section
* Blog / devotionals
* Volunteer signup form
* Member login area
* Testimonies page
✅ The final website should feel like a digital extension of the church—peaceful, welcoming, informative, and spiritually uplifting.‬"><span dir="ltr" class="x1iyjqo2 x6ikm8r x10wlt62 x1n2onr6 xlyipyv xuxw1ft x1rg5ohu _ao3e" style="min-height: 0px;">Create a modern, responsive, and accessible church website that reflects a welcoming, peaceful, and spiritual atmosphere. The design should use soft colors, elegant typography, and meaningful imagery (cross, Bible, prayer, worship, community).
The website must be mobile-friendly, fast-loading, and easy to navigate for all age groups.
