&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;* “Join Us This Sunday” button
* Welcome message from the pastor
* Upcoming events preview
* Quick links to sermons, prayer requests, and contact
2. About Us
* Church history
* Vision and mission
* Statement of faith
* Leadership team (pastor, ministers, staff)
3. Ministries
Separate sections for:
* Youth ministry
* Women’s fellowship
* Men’s fellowship
* Children’s ministry
* Outreach / missions
Each ministry should have a short description and meeting details.
4. Sermons
* Sermon archive with:
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;* Title
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;* Speaker
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;* Date
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;* Bible passage
* Audio/video player
* Download option
* Search and filter by topic or book of the Bible
5. Events
* Upcoming events calendar
* Special services (Christmas, Easter, conferences, fasting prayer)
* Registration form for events
6. Gallery
* Photos of:
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;* Worship services
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;* Baptism
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;* Outreach programs
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;* Church gatherings
7. Prayer Request
* Secure form to submit prayer requests
* Option to mark as private
* Message: “We will pray for you”
8. Give / Donations
* Online giving options
* UPI / bank details
* Tithes and offerings information
* Scripture on giving
9. Contact Us
* Church address with Google Map
* Phone number
* Email
* Service timings
* Contact form
<img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="⚙️" draggable="false" class="b4 emoji wa  _ao3e" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: -60px -20px;"> Functional Requirements
* Mobile responsive design
* SEO-friendly structure
* Fast loading speed
* Social media links
* Newsletter subscription
* WhatsApp “Message Us” button
* Live streaming integration (YouTube/Facebook)
<img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="🔒" draggable="false" class="b76 emoji wa  _ao3e" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: -20px -40px;"> Accessibility &amp; UX
* Large readable fonts
* Alt text for images
* Simple navigation for elderly users
* Clear call-to-action buttons
<img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="📝" draggable="false" class="b74 emoji wa  _ao3e" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: -80px -20px;"> Content Tone
* Warm, welcoming, and faith-centered
* Scripture-based messaging
* Community-focused language
* Encouraging and inclusive
<img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="💻" draggable="false" class="b73 emoji wa  _ao3e" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: 0px 0px;"> Technical Suggestions (Optional)
If coding:
* Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (or React)
* Backend: Node.js / Django / PHP
* CMS option: WordPress for easy sermon uploads
* Database for sermons, events, and prayer requests
<img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="📌" draggable="false" class="b73 emoji wa  _ao3e" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: -40px -60px;"> Extra Features (Optional but Recommended)
